[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[background arg="res://DialogicStuff/backgroundLevel6Part3.png" fade="0.0"]
join Rose (Rose_Angry2) leftmost
join Mary (Mary_serious) rightmost
join HeartHoarder center
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder1.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: So, you've discovered the truth in those old records...
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Rose1.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose: The messages we found... You and Grandpa were in contact!
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Mary1.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: You spent years working together on the Heart Engine...
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder2.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Your grandfather and I communicated through satellite signals.
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder3.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Your grandfather was brilliant. We believed we could change everything.
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder4.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: With the Heart Engine, we created a revolutionary machine, capable of immense amounts of clean energy.
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder5.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: The prototype worked perfectly, powering portals between distant worlds.
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder6.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: However, when Earth's governments found out about it, they couldn't leave us alone.
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder7.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: The plans, the prototype, all our work, stolen! And then...
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder8.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: And then they invaded Valeria...
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder9.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: My family was at the research facility. My wife, my children... When your forces came through...
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Mary2.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: wait, you're saying that...
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Rose2.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose (Rose_confused): We were the invaders?
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder10.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Yes... You humans. You pests invaded my homeland, all due to the disgusting greed that possesses all of you.
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder11.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: In order to win the war, I had to make modifications to the only remaining Heart Engine I had in my arsenal.
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Rose3.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose (Rose_Angry2): Instead of a clean source of energy, you sacrificed your own people for fuel.
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder12.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Yes... you remember. And now I am here, with our roles reversed.
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Mary3.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: I don't understand. After the war, why not revert back to the original design of the Heart Engine?
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder13.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: If only it were that simple. Some choices... can't be undone.
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Mary4.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary: So you are invading Earth for revenge...
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder14.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Your grandfather saw this coming. Why else would he build Guardian?
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Rose4.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose: Maybe he built it hoping someone would stop this cycle of revenge!
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder15.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Too late for that. Earth will pay for what they've done. Every. Last. Soul.
[style name="visualNovelMary"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Mary5.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Mary (Mary_serious): We won't let you continue this!
[style name="visualNovelRose"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/Rose5.ogg" volume="0.0"]
Rose: We will stop you!
[style name="VisualNovelHeartHoarder"]
[voice path="res://DialogicStuff/Audio/voiceLines/Level6HeartHoarderIntro/HeartHoarder16.ogg" volume="0.0"]
HeartHoarder: Oh it will. Follow me through the portal, and meet your end.
